{
  "swagger": "2.0",
  "info": {
    "description": "\n# Introduction\n\nWelcome to the UnificationEngine® Line API! You can use our API to access UnificationEngine® API endpoints, which can communicate with line. You can even create your own connector and link it with UnificationEngine® in the [developer portal](https://developer.unificationengine.com/)\n",
